<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Meu Futuro com a Matemática</title>

  <!-- Fonte -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe, #f1f5f9);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .container {
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 500px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #1e3a8a;
    }

    .tabs {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .tab {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 10px;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: 0.3s;
      margin: 0 5px;
      background: #e2e8f0;
    }

    .tab:hover {
      background: #cbd5f5;
    }

    .tab.active {
      background: #3b82f6;
      color: white;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .content {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(10px);
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
      display: none;
    }

    .content.active {
      display: block;
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #334155;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    @media (max-width: 500px) {
      .tabs {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .tab {
        margin: 5px 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="container">
    <h1>📊 Meu Futuro com a Matemática</h1>

    <div class="tabs">
      <div class="tab active" onclick="openTab(0)">🎓 Faculdade</div>
      <div class="tab" onclick="openTab(1)">📚 Colégio</div>
      <div class="tab" onclick="openTab(2)">💼 Emprego</div>
    </div>

    <div class="content active">
      <p><strong>Objetivo:</strong> Entrar em uma faculdade.<br>
      <strong>Prazo:</strong> Até o ano que vem.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p><strong>Objetivo:</strong> Concluir o ensino médio.<br>
      <strong>Prazo:</strong> Até o final deste ano.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p><strong>Objetivo:</strong> Conseguir um emprego estável.<br>
      <strong>Prazo:</strong> Até o ano que vem.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <script>
    function openTab(index) {
      let tabs = document.querySelectorAll(".tab");
      let contents = document.querySelectorAll(".content");

      tabs.forEach(tab => tab.classList.remove("active"));
      contents.forEach(content => content.classList.remove("active"));

      tabs[index].classList.add("active");
      contents[index].classList.add("active");
    }
  </script>

</body>
</html>
